{
  "chapter": 24,
  "chapter_summary": "第二十四回\"死中求活\"：小鱼儿以满身毒蛇吓昏慕容九妹、吓跑小仙女，却与铁心兰争执是否该杀慕容九妹。花无缺及时出现制止，二人展开一场关于男子汉气概与道德立场的辩论。花无缺的侍女荷露与圆脸少女带走铁心兰，慕容九妹梦呓间泄露小鱼儿真名。花无缺闻之色变，坦言受师父之命必须亲手杀死江小鱼。小鱼儿假意以匕首自刎威胁，趁花无缺犹豫之际假摔坠崖，实则以尖刀插入峭壁、攀住山藤逃生。铁心兰悲痛欲绝欲随小鱼儿跳崖，花无缺柔声劝阻。慕容九妹神智恍惚出现，宣称自己曾亲手杀死小鱼儿。本章揭示花无缺奉移花宫之命追杀小鱼儿的核心矛盾，小鱼儿以智谋化解危机，死中求活。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "慕容九妹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "蛇兄呀蛇兄，无论你以后是否会害死我，我都得谢谢你，无论如何，你至少已救过我两次命了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 19,
      "line_end": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你几时被慕容姑娘害死过？什么淹死鬼，烫死鬼，我……我简直被你弄糊涂了。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 23,
      "line_end": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "女孩子还是糊涂些好，女孩子知道得越多，麻烦就越多，你只要知道我有两下子就行了。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 27,
      "line_end": 27
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你实在是有两下子，慕容九妹居然会被你吓晕，小仙女居然会被你吓得落荒而逃，这种事告诉别人，别人只怕也不会相信的。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 31,
      "line_end": 31
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "依你看，我会对她怎么样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 33,
      "line_end": 33
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你就任凭她晕在这里，一走了之。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 35,
      "line_end": 35
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "或者……或者你用藤子捆住她，等她醒来时，打她几下出气。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 37,
      "line_end": 37
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "妇人之仁，到底是妇人之言。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 39,
      "line_end": 39
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "这……这么凶的法子还不够？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 41,
      "line_end": 41
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "当然不够。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 43,
      "line_end": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "难道……难道你真要杀了她？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 45,
      "line_end": 47
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "我若不杀她，难道还等她以后来杀我不成？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 49,
      "line_end": 49
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我实在想不到你……你……你竟真的如此狠心。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 51,
      "line_end": 51
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "你现在总该想到了吧！你若不愿瞧，就走得远远好了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 53,
      "line_end": 53
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "text": "你这个狠心的女人，我若不杀了你，怎对得住自己。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 59,
      "line_end": 59
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "text": "我正好要毒蛇咬你一口，看着究竟是蛇毒，还是你毒。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 63,
      "line_end": 63
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "text": "什么事你都怨不得我，你若不想杀我，我绝不会杀你的……",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 75,
      "line_end": 75
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "以这样的手段来杀一个女孩子，岂非有失男子汉的身分。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 77,
      "line_end": 77
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 79,
      "line_end": 79
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你是说我杀不得她？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 83,
      "line_end": 83
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "一个男人，对女孩子总该客气些，就算她有什么对不起你的事，你也该瞧在她是个女人份上，让她一些。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 85,
      "line_end": 85
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "好个温柔体贴的花公子，世上有你这样的男人，当真是女人的福气，天下的女人真该联合起来送你一面锦旗才是。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 87,
      "line_end": 89
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "好说好说。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 91,
      "line_end": 93
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "但女人若要杀死你时，你又如何？难道你就闭起眼睛来让她们杀？难道你连还手都不还手？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 95,
      "line_end": 95
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我若做了对不起她的事，被她杀死，也绝无怨言。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 97,
      "line_end": 97
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "但若有个女人做了对不起你的事，你不杀她？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 99,
      "line_end": 99
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "男人总该让着女人些才是。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 101,
      "line_end": 101
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你这样的想法，真不知从哪里学来的。照你这样说来，天下的男人简直都该死了，都该一头跳进黄河才是。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 103,
      "line_end": 105
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "那也不必。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 107,
      "line_end": 107
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你的意思，是定要我放了她？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 113,
      "line_end": 113
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "足下放了她才是英雄所为。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 115,
      "line_end": 117
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "我今日放了她，她日后若来杀我，又当如何？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 119,
      "line_end": 119
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "日后之事，谁也无法预测，是么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 121,
      "line_end": 121
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "好，我要杀她，我就不是英雄，不是男子汉，我就该死，但她若要杀我，却是天经地义的事，我被她杀了也是活该，是么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 123,
      "line_end": 123
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "在下并无此意，只是……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 125,
      "line_end": 127
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "我不管你是什么意思，今天我打不过你，你放个屁我也只有听着，但以后你打不过我时，我偏偏要杀几个女人让你瞧瞧。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 129,
      "line_end": 131
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "text": "算你厉害，你抬走吧！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 133,
      "line_end": 133
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "如此就多谢了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 135,
      "line_end": 137
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_lian_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "圆脸少女",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "今天若非公子在这里，我就宰了你，让你知道女人的厉害。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 141,
      "line_end": 143
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_yuan_lian_shao_nv",
      "text": "随便你吧！骂什么都没关系，因为你是女人，女人天生就可以骂男人的。花公子，你说是么？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 145,
      "line_end": 147
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "能被女人骂的男人，才算是福气，有些男人，女人连骂都不屑骂的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 149,
      "line_end": 151
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "哈……哈哈，如此说采，我真是荣幸之至，为了免得让你难受，他日也得找几个女人来让你荣幸荣幸才是。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 153,
      "line_end": 153
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "那时在下必定洗耳恭听。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 155,
      "line_end": 157
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_lu",
      "speaker_name": "荷露",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "姑娘，你也跟咱们一起走吧。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 161,
      "line_end": 161
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_he_lu",
      "text": "我……我……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 163,
      "line_end": 163
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_lian_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "圆脸少女",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "那种男人，你还要理他么，跟咱们走吧！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 167,
      "line_end": 167
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_lu",
      "speaker_name": "荷露",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "我家公子也正想和你聊聊。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 169,
      "line_end": 171
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "去去去，你快跟他们去吧！我现在虽然倒霉，但还没什么，你若再跟着我，我才是倒霉透顶了。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 173,
      "line_end": 175
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "慕容九妹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小鱼儿……江小鱼，放了我……放了我吧！",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 181,
      "line_end": 181
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你就是江小鱼，就是小鱼儿？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 183,
      "line_end": 183
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "我这名字很出名么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 185,
      "line_end": 185
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "抱歉得很……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 187,
      "line_end": 187
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "抱歉？你为什么抱歉？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 189,
      "line_end": 189
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "只因我要杀死你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 191,
      "line_end": 191
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你头脑有些不正常么？怎地突然又要杀我？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 195,
      "line_end": 195
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "只因你是江小鱼，所以我要杀你。芸芸天下只有一个是我要杀的人，那人就是江小鱼，就是你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 197,
      "line_end": 197
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "我懂了，可是有人叫你杀我的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 199,
      "line_end": 201
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "正是家师所命。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 203,
      "line_end": 203
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你师父为什么要你杀他？为什么？……为什么？……",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 205,
      "line_end": 205
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "很好，我本来也想杀死你的，只因我目前实在打不过你，所以才一直忍住，不过，现在……",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 209,
      "line_end": 211
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "喂，可是你救了我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 253,
      "line_end": 253
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 255,
      "line_end": 255
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "那么厉害的蛇毒，你也能救？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 257,
      "line_end": 257
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "这仙子香与你已服下的素女丹，万毒俱都可解。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 259,
      "line_end": 259
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你方才不是要杀我的么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 261,
      "line_end": 261
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我现在还是要杀你，只因我必须亲手杀死你，不能让你因为别的事而死。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 263,
      "line_end": 263
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你为何定要亲手杀死我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 265,
      "line_end": 265
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "只因我受命如此。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 267,
      "line_end": 267
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "她一定要你亲手杀死我？我死在别的人，别的事上都不行，这……你不觉奇怪么？你不问是为了什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 269,
      "line_end": 269
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我不必问。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 271,
      "line_end": 271
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "看来你倒听话得很。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 273,
      "line_end": 273
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "本宫令严，无人敢违。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 275,
      "line_end": 275
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "看来你也老实得很，我问你什么，你就答什么。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 277,
      "line_end": 277
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "任何人无论问我什么，我都会据实以告，我纵要杀死你，但那和问答的话完全是两回事。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 279,
      "line_end": 279
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你非要亲手杀死我不可？我若杀死了你呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 281,
      "line_end": 281
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你杀不死我的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 283,
      "line_end": 283
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你敢和我拼一拼么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 285,
      "line_end": 285
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我正是要堂堂正正取你性命。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 287,
      "line_end": 287
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "好，你先退后几步，先让我起来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 289,
      "line_end": 289
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你这人实在太老实了，但我却不知你是真的老实，还是假的老实，也许你自以为对什么事都太有把握．所以随便怎样都无所谓。",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 293,
      "line_end": 295
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你要我死，那并不困难，但你若定要亲手杀死我，今生今世，再也休想。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 301,
      "line_end": 303
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你……你这是做什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 307,
      "line_end": 307
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "只要你身子向我这边动一动，我这一刀就刺下去，那么你就一辈子也休想亲手杀死我了，因为我已亲手杀死了自己。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 309,
      "line_end": 311
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你若还想亲手杀死我，现在就得忍耐，莫要动……一动都莫要动……",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 323,
      "line_end": 323
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "是谁在惊呼，是不是他？……是不是他？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 353,
      "line_end": 353
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "他——他在哪里？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 357,
      "line_end": 357
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "——你——你——你杀了他——你杀了他！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 361,
      "line_end": 363
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "我并没有杀他，只是他——他自己失足落下了悬崖。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 369,
      "line_end": 371
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你——你真的没有杀他？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 373,
      "line_end": 373
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "我一生之中，绝不说半句假话。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 375,
      "line_end": 375
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "那你为什么不还手？",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 377,
      "line_end": 377
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "我知道你此刻心里必定很难受，你纵然伤了我，也是理所应当的，我绝不会怪你的。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 379,
      "line_end": 381
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "铁姑娘，你还是歇歇去吧，你——",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 385,
      "line_end": 385
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "是——我是该歇歇去了，是该去了——",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 387,
      "line_end": 387
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "小鱼儿，你等着，我来陪你一起歇歇——",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 389,
      "line_end": 389
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "放开我——放开我——为什么不让我下去陪他，他一个人死在下面，是多么寂寞——",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 393,
      "line_end": 393
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "慕容九妹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁死在下面了——？一个人能寂寂寞寞，安安静静地死，是多么幸福。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 395,
      "line_end": 395
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "text": "小鱼儿终于已死了，你开心么——？他就死在这悬崖下，你可要去瞧瞧他死时的模样？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 401,
      "line_end": 401
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "慕容九妹",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "他不会死在这里的，死在这里的，绝不是他。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 403,
      "line_end": 403
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "慕容九妹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他早已死在慕容山庄了，是我亲手杀死了他——一个人是绝不可能死两次的，你们说是么——是么？",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 407,
      "line_end": 407
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_he_lu",
      "text": "荷露，这位姑娘方才被骇得太厉害了，到此刻神智还未恢复，你扶她回屋去躺躺吧！",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 411,
      "line_end": 413
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_jiu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "慕容九妹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我亲手杀死了他，我亲眼瞧见了他的鬼魂。哈哈，你们瞧见过鬼么——你们能亲手杀死他么？",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 415,
      "line_end": 417
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们谁也杀不死他，世上惟一能杀死他的人，就是他自己——",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 419,
      "line_end": 421
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但他终于杀死了自己——他终于毁灭了自己——为什么聪明的人，总是会自己毁自己——",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 423,
      "line_end": 423
    }
  ],
